## MULTI-TENANT ARCHITECTURE				
Organization (Tenant/Client) → Account (Business Unit) → Department → User				
- **Hierarchy validation (mandatory)**: **Account** must belong to **Organization**; **Department** must belong to **Account**; **User** must belong to **Department** — enforce on create/update via **`HierarchyValidator`** (`backend/src/common/validators/hierarchy.validator.ts`)				
- **Tenant admin dashboard**: tree view of **Org → Accounts → Departments → Users** with **counts at each level** — **`GET /api/v1/organization/hierarchy`** (JWT org scope, **`org_admin`**)				
- **User** belongs to **Department** (and therefore **`account_id`** + **`org_id`**); **role** and **permissions** govern access; credentials stored as **`password_hash`** only (**Argon2id** via **`PasswordService`**; **zxcvbn** score ≥ **3** on registration/password update; **no passwords in logs**; weak/legacy login sets **`password_change_required`**)				
- **Department** belongs to **Account** (and therefore **`org_id`** + **`account_id`**); **OKRs** are assigned at **department** level				
- **Account** belongs to **Organization** (`org_id`); **budget** per account — **credit limit** (optional cap on allocation, may exceed allocated), **allocated** / **available** / **used** (usage tracked per account; consumption cannot exceed **available**); **`account_budgets`** materialized view + **`AccountBudgetService`**; org admin **`GET /api/v1/accounts/:id/budget`**, **`POST …/budget/allocate`**, **`PATCH …/budget/limit`**; dashboard **`AccountBudgetDashboard`**; **multiple accounts per organization**
- **Credits** are the **consumption currency**. **Full audit trail** in immutable **`credit_transactions`** ledger — **`GET /api/v1/credits/transactions`** (filter by **type**, **date**, **account**; pagination); **`GET …/transactions/summary`** (aggregations by type/account/daily); **`GET …/transactions/export`** (CSV); dashboard **`CreditTransactionHistory`** (charts + table). **Low-balance alerts** at **25% / 10% / 5%** remaining (configurable thresholds); **email** (SendGrid) and **in-app** (Redis pub/sub **`notifications`** channel); respects org **notification preferences**; checked after each consumption — **`CreditAlertService`**, **`GET/PUT /api/v1/credits/alerts/settings`**. Each **org** has one **`credits`** balance record (**`balance`**, **`reserved`** for pending ops); **decremented on usage** via **`CreditService`**; immutable ledger in **`credit_transactions`**; atomic balance updates use **MongoDB transactions** — **`backend/src/modules/credits/`** (`**CreditModel**`, **`CreditService**`). **Buy credits via Stripe** — org admin **`POST /api/v1/credits/purchase`** (**PaymentIntent**, **$0.01/credit**); **credits added to org balance immediately** on **`payment_intent.succeeded`** webhook (**`CreditPurchaseService`**); frontend **`CreditPurchaseForm`** (Stripe Elements). **Allocate to accounts** — org admin **`POST /api/v1/accounts/:id/allocate`** moves credits from **org pool** to account **`budget.allocated_credits`**; **account cannot exceed `credit_limit`** when limit &gt; 0 (**`CreditAllocationService`**, MongoDB transaction). **Track usage** — **signals** (1), **actions** / execution (5), **HITL** (2) credits via **`CreditConsumptionService`**; deducts **`budget.used_credits`** on account (available = allocated − used); **real-time** ledger + optional Timescale **`credit_usage`** / **`hitl_decisions`**; integrated in **`SignalService`**, **`ExecutionService`**, **`HitlService`** (BullMQ workers). **Rate card** — **`backend/src/config/credit-rates.ts`** **`DEFAULT_RATES`**; org admin **`GET /api/v1/credits/rates`**; **display rate card** in dashboard (**`CreditRateCard`**); **enterprise custom rates** via platform admin **`PUT /api/organizations/:id/credit-rates`** (`org_settings` key **`credit_rates`**, **`CreditRatesService`**)				
- **Subscription plans** — **`backend/src/config/plans.ts`** **`PLANS`** (**starter** / **pro** / **enterprise**): **monthly_credits**, **features**, **price_monthly** / **price_annual**, **max_accounts**, **max_users**; **`GET /api/v1/plans`** catalog; **`GET /api/v1/plans/current`** + **`POST /api/v1/plans/change`** (upgrade/downgrade, Stripe proration when configured); **`PlanLimitsValidator`** enforces caps on account/user create; org **`subscription.tier`** + **`settings.features`**				
- **Stripe billing** — **Stripe** for payments; **sync plans** with Stripe Products/Prices (**`starter_monthly`**, **`starter_annual`**, **`pro_monthly`**, **`pro_annual`**, **`enterprise_annual`**); **webhook** **`POST /api/billing/stripe/webhook`** — **`invoice.paid`** → allocate org **`billing.allocated_credits`**; **`invoice.payment_failed`** → notify + **suspend** org; **`customer.subscription.deleted`** → deactivate + terminate contract; **`stripe.customer_id`** / **`price_ids`** on **Organization** — **`backend/src/modules/billing/`** (`**StripeService**`, platform **`POST /api/billing/stripe/catalog/sync`**)				
- **Usage dashboard** (org admin) — **`GET /api/v1/usage/summary`**: **credits used vs allocated**, **breakdown by account** (Timescale **`credit_usage`**), **usage trends** (daily); **`UsageService`** (`backend/src/modules/billing/usage.service.ts`); frontend **`UsageDashboard`** (`src/components/UsageDashboard.tsx`)				
